Dialogue: 100,0:00:05.98,0:00:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Mystery!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:08.73,0:00:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystery? That's different from the usual.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:12.32,0:00:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our sixth extra, after all.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:14.49,0:00:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't get ourselves in a rut.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:16.12,0:00:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, let's drop the meta discussion.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:18.41,0:00:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem with it?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.70,0:00:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just thought you were \Ngoing to strip again.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:24.25,0:00:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, a running gag is only funny twice.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:27.21,0:00:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.00,0:00:31.42,Default,,0,0,5,,All right, let's get this installment started!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:31.42,0:00:32.67,Default,,0,0,5,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.67,0:00:33.97,Default,,0,0,5,,Here we go...{I mean, I'm hearing "I'm worried"... -Starfish}
Dialogue: 100,0:00:33.97,0:00:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\c&H000000&\t(22,356,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Two-hour Suspense Dragon!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.85,0:00:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Lucoa, you are the culprit.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:43.31,0:00:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous. Do you have\Nany proof that I'm the culprit?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:47.56,0:00:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this sort of scene is common.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.86,0:00:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You showed up on the surveillance footage!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:52.82,0:00:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fleeing the scene completely naked!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:55.49,0:00:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, no!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.95,0:00:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you {\i1}just{\i0} say you \Nwere gonna stay dressed?!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.45,0:01:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(26,360,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Closed Circle!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:03.91,0:01:08.38,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,I-Is it really you? The rising star in the world of detectives,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.38,0:01:13.30,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,the famed high school girl detective, \NLady Kobayashi Tohru?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.30,0:01:18.59,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,It is. But never mind me. \NUntil we can identify the killer,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.59,0:01:20.60,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,we should all sleep together tonight.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.60,0:01:21.47,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:21.47,0:01:25.52,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Since we don't know where the killer may be lurking, we should be cautious.
