Dialogue: 100,0:01:28.81,0:01:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(29,362,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Locked Room Trick!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.07,0:01:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit used some kind of \Nblunt weapon to kill Lady Lucoa.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.74,0:01:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this room has been locked.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.82,0:01:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A locked room? Are you really sure about that?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:40.95,0:01:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you use a magic portal like this,\Ncoming and going is a simple matter.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.75,0:01:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, anyway.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.83,0:01:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(27,360,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Timetable Trick!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:52.21,0:01:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Tohru, we won't reach the scene\Nof the crime in time on this train.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:56.84,0:01:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! If one were to...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:59.80,0:02:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:00.68,0:02:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do this, we have plenty of time \Nto reach the crime scene.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, {\i1}you{\i0} can do that.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.18,0:02:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(29,363,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Threatening Letter!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.19,0:02:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Shouta's been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.86,0:02:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Tohru, a threatening letter\Nfrom the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.53,0:02:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"You won't get away. \NWherever you go, I will be watching.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.66,0:02:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All that is yours will soon be mine. \NIn time, even your heart will belong to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:23.62,0:02:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Say your prayers, Miss Kobayashi."
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.04,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This is the love letter I wrote yesterday!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.50,0:02:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't have a stamp, so it was returned.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a seriously scary love letter...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(25,359,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Holmes!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.76,0:02:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be a client. Come in.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.55,0:02:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon my intrusion.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:42.05,0:02:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for saying so, \Nbut you rushed here straight from your tub.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How can you tell?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:48.18,0:02:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair is somewhat damp,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,your skin is sweaty,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and the biggest clue...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.69,0:02:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You not having any clothes on\Nprovides undeniable proof!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:57.90,0:03:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah, yeah, she's naked, she's naked.\NWhatever floats your boat.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.45,0:03:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, it happened again. What a shocker.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next time will be our final feature.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finally ending this?
Comment: 100,0:01:44.87,0:01:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...